[SPEAKER_00] jer mjesto na kojem stojiš, sve to je mjesto.

188
00:17:31,980 --> 00:17:39,279
[SPEAKER_00] Svaki put kada se zagovaratelj približi Bogu,

189
00:17:39,279 --> 00:17:42,480
[SPEAKER_00] gospodin nas pocijeća

190
00:17:42,480 --> 00:17:46,319
[SPEAKER_00] kako trebamo izuti obuću,

191
00:17:46,319 --> 00:17:50,500
[SPEAKER_00] jer se nalazimo na svetom mjestu.

192
00:17:50,579 --> 00:17:58,960
[SPEAKER_00] jer dok zagovaramo, molimo u snazi Duha Svetoga,

193
00:17:58,960 --> 00:18:03,119
[SPEAKER_01] preko Isusa Hrista koji zagovara,

194
00:18:03,119 --> 00:18:07,799
[SPEAKER_00] i mi svoje molotve upućujemo Otcu.

195
00:18:07,799 --> 00:18:19,440
[SPEAKER_00] i tako se zagovaratelj povezuje i sjedinjuje s tri osobe presvetog trojstva.

196
00:18:19,440 --> 00:18:28,119
[SPEAKER_00] I prva stvar koju bi vam želio reći

197
00:18:28,119 --> 00:18:31,259
[SPEAKER_01] odnosi se na samo središte zagovaranja,

198
00:18:31,259 --> 00:18:48,220
[SPEAKER_00] Revelations, chapter 2, verses 2 to 5.

199
00:18:48,220 --> 00:18:53,460
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, knjiga Otkrivenja, drugo poglavlje, redak 2 do 4.

200
00:18:53,460 --> 00:18:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] I will read.

201
00:18:56,900 --> 00:19:02,980
[SPEAKER_01] Znam tvoja dijela, tvoj trud i postojanost tvoju,

202
00:19:02,980 --> 00:19:06,079
[SPEAKER_01] i da ne možeš podnijeti opak ih.

203
00:19:06,579 --> 00:19:10,079
[SPEAKER_01] Iskušao si one koji se prave apostolima, a nisu,

204
00:19:10,079 --> 00:19:12,380
[SPEAKER_01] i otkrio si da su lažljivci.

205
00:19:12,380 --> 00:19:16,200
[SPEAKER_01] Postojan si, podnio si za ime moje,

206
00:19:16,200 --> 00:19:18,019
[SPEAKER_01] i nisi smalaksao.

207
00:19:18,019 --> 00:19:20,079
[SPEAKER_01] Ali imam protiv tebe.

208
00:19:20,079 --> 00:19:22,839
[SPEAKER_01] Prvu si ljubav svoju ostavio.

209
00:19:24,000 --> 00:19:26,119
[SPEAKER_01] Spomeni se dakle, odakle si pao,

210
00:19:26,119 --> 00:19:29,039
[SPEAKER_01] obrati se i čini prva dijela.

211
00:19:29,039 --> 00:19:33,119
[SPEAKER_00] Now, it begins like this.

212
00:19:33,119 --> 00:19:34,420
[SPEAKER_01] Počinje ovako.

213
00:19:34,420 --> 00:19:35,960
[SPEAKER_01] I know your works.

214
00:19:35,960 --> 00:19:37,680
[SPEAKER_01] Znam tvoja dijela.

215
00:19:37,680 --> 00:19:39,279
[SPEAKER_01] Your hard labor.

216
00:19:39,279 --> 00:19:40,839
[SPEAKER_01] Znam tvoj trud.

217
00:19:40,839 --> 00:19:42,140
[SPEAKER_01] Your endivarence.

218
00:19:42,140 --> 00:19:43,920
[SPEAKER_01] Znam postojanost tvoju.

219
00:19:43,920 --> 00:19:46,980
[SPEAKER_00] And you have been doing a marvelous job.

220
00:19:46,980 --> 00:19:50,019
[SPEAKER_00] I obavljao si izvrstan posao.

221
00:19:50,380 --> 00:19:58,799
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ovo je pismo koje je bilo upućeno crkvi u Efezu.

222
00:19:58,799 --> 00:20:07,039
[SPEAKER_00] I već znamo od prvog poglavlja knjige Otkrivenja

223
00:20:07,039 --> 00:20:09,460
[SPEAKER_01] da je Sveti Ivan bio pisac ove knjige.

224
00:20:09,460 --> 00:20:17,039
[SPEAKER_00] I on piše ovo pismo.

225
00:20:18,980 --> 00:20:20,460
[SPEAKER_01] Upućeno je sedam crkava.

226
00:20:20,460 --> 00:20:25,680
[SPEAKER_00] I on opisuje svoje iskustvo.

227
00:20:25,680 --> 00:20:32,740
[SPEAKER_00] I rekao je kako je sjedio na jednom otoku.

228
00:20:32,740 --> 00:20:42,099
[SPEAKER_00] I odjednom sam se okrenuo i čuo sam glas koji je mi je govorio.

229
00:20:42,359 --> 00:20:47,420
[SPEAKER_01] i taj glas mi je rekao da piši ovo pismo.

230
00:20:47,420 --> 00:20:56,420
[SPEAKER_00] I prvo od tih pisama je pismo crkvi u Efezu.

231
00:20:56,920 --> 00:21:09,039
[SPEAKER_00] 25 godina nakon što je vjera stigla u Efezu, on piše ovo pismo.

232
00:21:09,119 --> 00:21:22,920
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, taj prvi dio pismo je više kao potvrda, potvrda svega što su oni već znali.

233
00:21:22,920 --> 00:21:30,180
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to je već potvrda onoga svega s čime su se oni složili.

234
00:21:30,180 --> 00:21:34,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ali nakon toga kaže,

235
00:21:34,680 --> 00:21:39,039
[SPEAKER_01] četreti redak,

236
00:21:39,039 --> 00:21:44,440
[SPEAKER_00] ali imam protiv tebe.

237
00:21:44,440 --> 00:21:53,339
[SPEAKER_00] Prvu si ljubav svoju ostavio.

238
00:21:53,339 --> 00:22:03,619
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, 25 godina nakon što je vjera došla u Efezu,

239
00:22:03,619 --> 00:22:11,339
[SPEAKER_00] Duh Božji se obraća crkvi u Efezu

240
00:22:11,339 --> 00:22:19,380
[SPEAKER_01] i kaže im, radili ste izvrsne, prekrasne stvari.

241
00:22:19,380 --> 00:22:24,880
[SPEAKER_01] Stvarno cijenim sav trud koji ste unijeli u to.

242
00:22:24,880 --> 00:22:33,599
[SPEAKER_00] Stvarno cijenim činjenicu da ste 25 godina iz 25 godina.

243
00:22:33,619 --> 00:22:35,380
[SPEAKER_01] želi u postojanosti svoje vjere.

244
00:22:35,380 --> 00:22:39,019
[SPEAKER_00] Yet, I have this against you.

245
00:22:39,019 --> 00:22:42,519
[SPEAKER_01] And what is it?

246
00:22:42,519 --> 00:22:51,339
[SPEAKER_00] That you lost the love you had at first.

247
00:22:51,339 --> 00:22:53,339
[SPEAKER_00] Izgubili ste svoju prvu ljubav.

248
00:22:53,339 --> 00:23:00,279
[SPEAKER_01] Kada ste počeli, kada ste došli na život,

249
00:23:00,279 --> 00:23:04,759
[SPEAKER_01] Gospodin nam to govori danas.

250
00:23:04,759 --> 00:23:12,720
[SPEAKER_01] Kada ste vi započeli, kakva je bila vaša ljubav prema meni?

251
00:23:12,940 --> 00:23:16,759
[SPEAKER_01] Kada ste me prvi put upoznali,

252
00:23:16,759 --> 00:23:21,880
[SPEAKER_01] Možda je to bilo na seminaru obnove u Duhu,

253
00:23:21,880 --> 00:23:27,759
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon što ste iskusili krštenje u Duhu svetom,

254
00:23:27,759 --> 00:23:33,059
[SPEAKER_01] Gorili ste od ljubavi za mene.

255
00:23:33,059 --> 00:23:36,819
[SPEAKER_00] Bili ste jako strastveni.

256
00:23:36,819 --> 00:23:47,480
[SPEAKER_00] I sjećam se svog prvog iskustva seminara obnove krštenja u Duhu.

257
00:23:47,539 --> 00:23:50,960
[SPEAKER_01] I kada sam se vratio doma,

258
00:23:50,960 --> 00:23:56,940
[SPEAKER_00] Osjećao sam se kao da sam lebdio.

259
00:23:56,940 --> 00:24:03,140
[SPEAKER_01] Mao sam dojam da sam najsvetiji čovjek na zemlji.

260
00:24:03,140 --> 00:24:08,099
[SPEAKER_00] To je bilo tako jako, jako iskustvo.

261
00:24:08,099 --> 00:24:14,380
[SPEAKER_00] Moje srce je gorjelo od ljubavi prema Bogu.

262
00:24:14,380 --> 00:24:21,960
[SPEAKER_01] I oni svi kažu kako je ta prva ljubav luda ljubav.

263
00:24:21,960 --> 00:24:25,059
[SPEAKER_01] Ta ljubav je strastvena.

264
00:24:25,059 --> 00:24:28,900
[SPEAKER_00] Neki od vas se čak smiju.

265
00:24:28,900 --> 00:24:33,920
[SPEAKER_01] Jer oni znaju i razumiju što znači prva ljubav.

266
00:24:33,920 --> 00:24:38,180
[SPEAKER_00] Prva ljubav je nešto jako posebno.

267
00:24:38,180 --> 00:24:42,180
[SPEAKER_01] I ta ljubav nam kaže,

268
00:24:42,519 --> 00:24:45,759
[SPEAKER_01] sjeti se te prve ljubavi.

269
00:24:45,759 --> 00:24:51,779
[SPEAKER_01] Sjeti se onog dana kada si započeo.

270
00:24:51,779 --> 00:24:56,099
[SPEAKER_01] Sjeti se onog dana kada si me isprva upoznal.

271
00:24:56,099 --> 00:25:03,059
[SPEAKER_01] Sjeti se svog osobnog odnosa koji si imao s Isusom.

272
00:25:03,059 --> 00:25:06,559
[SPEAKER_01] kako smo bili strastveni.

273
00:25:06,559 --> 00:25:12,640
[SPEAKER_01] I kako smo, dakle, počeli strastveno, godljivo.

274
00:25:14,640 --> 00:25:17,500
[SPEAKER_01] kako smo se okrenuli prema Bogu.

275
00:25:17,500 --> 00:25:23,900
[SPEAKER_00] I u tom procesu smo započeli mnoge službe.

276
00:25:23,900 --> 00:25:28,400
[SPEAKER_01] Možda smo počeli, we began.

277
00:25:28,859 --> 00:25:32,160
[SPEAKER_00] počeli smo voditelji.

278
00:25:32,160 --> 00:25:36,660
[SPEAKER_01] I bili smo uključeni u svoje poslanje.

279
00:25:36,660 --> 00:25:39,819
[SPEAKER_00] Ali gospodin kaže,

280
00:25:40,200 --> 00:25:42,599
[SPEAKER_00] sa svim tim,

281
00:25:42,599 --> 00:25:50,240
[SPEAKER_00] sa svim tim što ste radili,

282
00:25:50,240 --> 00:25:51,819
[SPEAKER_01] polako ste izgubili

283
00:25:51,819 --> 00:25:53,839
[SPEAKER_01] izvida svoju prvu ljubav.

284
00:25:53,839 --> 00:26:01,279
[SPEAKER_00] To je nešto jako subtilno što se dogadi u našem životu.

285
00:26:01,279 --> 00:26:06,660
[SPEAKER_00] Dragi prijatelji,

286
00:26:06,660 --> 00:26:08,359
[SPEAKER_01] mi čak i ne svačavamo trenutak

287
00:26:08,359 --> 00:26:10,019
[SPEAKER_01] kada izgubimo tu prvu ljubav.

288
00:26:10,019 --> 00:26:14,400
[SPEAKER_00] Kad smo započeli,

289
00:26:14,400 --> 00:26:16,619
[SPEAKER_01] bili smo jako, jako, jako zagrijani.

290
00:26:16,619 --> 00:26:19,619
[SPEAKER_00] Bili smo jako vrući.

291
00:26:19,619 --> 00:26:24,880
[SPEAKER_00] I polako se počinjemo hladiti.

292
00:26:24,880 --> 00:26:27,559
[SPEAKER_01] A gospodin kaže,

293
00:26:27,980 --> 00:26:31,779
[SPEAKER_01] ako što ste bili vrući,

294
00:26:31,779 --> 00:26:35,220
[SPEAKER_01] onda kad postanete hladni,

295
00:26:35,220 --> 00:26:40,039
[SPEAKER_01] nećete postati jako hladni.

296
00:26:40,039 --> 00:26:44,220
[SPEAKER_01] Ostat ćete mlaki.

297
00:26:44,220 --> 00:26:48,880
[SPEAKER_01] I gospodin to naziva mlakošću.

298
00:26:48,880 --> 00:26:53,839
[SPEAKER_01] I u sljedećem poglavlju gospodin kaže,

299
00:26:54,200 --> 00:26:57,740
[SPEAKER_01] ispljenu ću te.

300
00:26:57,740 --> 00:27:01,680
[SPEAKER_01] Jer gospodin kaže,

301
00:27:01,680 --> 00:27:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] to mi se ne sviđa.

302
00:27:03,000 --> 00:27:09,160
[SPEAKER_00] I volio bih da si vruć ili da si hladan.

303
00:27:09,160 --> 00:27:15,579
[SPEAKER_01] Sada si u stanju koja je između toga dva stanja.

304
00:27:16,119 --> 00:27:18,880
[SPEAKER_01] Niti si vruć,

305
00:27:18,880 --> 00:27:21,400
[SPEAKER_01] niti si hladan.

306
00:27:21,400 --> 00:27:28,700
[SPEAKER_01] To je jako bitno za zagovaratelje.

307
00:27:28,700 --> 00:27:34,859
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, nitko ne može baš,

308
00:27:35,119 --> 00:27:39,140
[SPEAKER_01] ne može netko postati zagovaratelj.

309
00:27:39,140 --> 00:27:48,259
[SPEAKER_01] Osim ako vaše srce nije puno ljubavi za gospodina.

310
00:27:48,259 --> 00:27:53,240
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, moje pitanje je,

311
00:27:53,240 --> 00:27:55,299
[SPEAKER_01] zašto bi mi onda trebali zagovaratelj?

312
00:27:55,539 --> 00:28:00,859
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, zagovaranje nije baš skroz pogodno.

313
00:28:00,859 --> 00:28:05,400
