318
00:28:24,599 --> 00:28:27,859
[SPEAKER_01] Možda želite nedokreniti san.

319
00:28:27,859 --> 00:28:31,059
[SPEAKER_01] Možda želite otići u kino.

320
00:28:31,059 --> 00:28:36,680
[SPEAKER_00] A upravo je to vrijeme kada ćete zagovarati.

321
00:28:36,680 --> 00:28:42,339
[SPEAKER_00] i onda ćete dakle žrtvovati sve vaše odnose.

322
00:28:42,339 --> 00:28:45,500
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto biste to učinili?

323
00:28:45,500 --> 00:28:53,579
[SPEAKER_00] Samo ako ste osoba koja izgara od ljubavi za Boga.

324
00:28:53,579 --> 00:29:03,259
[SPEAKER_01] Samo ako ste osoba koja izgara od ljubavi za svoje sugrađane.

325
00:29:03,259 --> 00:29:07,599
[SPEAKER_00] Recimo, vi ste u Hrvatskoj,

326
00:29:07,599 --> 00:29:10,539
[SPEAKER_00] u Bosni i Hercegovini,

327
00:29:10,539 --> 00:29:18,259
[SPEAKER_01] dogodi se da vi zagovarate za nekoga tko živi u Sjedinjenim državama.

328
00:29:18,259 --> 00:29:25,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ta osoba nikad neće spoznati da ste vi zagovarali za nju.

329
00:29:25,599 --> 00:29:35,279
[SPEAKER_01] ta osoba nikad neće spoznati da ste vi bili ti koji ste zagovarali za nju ili za njega.

330
00:29:35,279 --> 00:29:43,480
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to je posao koji je bezvremenski.

331
00:29:43,819 --> 00:30:03,859
[SPEAKER_01] Zbog toga mi moramo imati srce pravog zagovaratelja.

332
00:30:03,859 --> 00:30:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] To srce je srce koje izgara od ljubavi za Gospodina.

333
00:30:14,000 --> 00:30:20,200
[SPEAKER_00] To je srce koje izgara od ljubavi za druge.

334
00:30:20,200 --> 00:30:24,440
[SPEAKER_01] I upravo zbog toga Gospodin kaže,

335
00:30:24,440 --> 00:30:29,920
[SPEAKER_00] izgubili ste svoju prvu ljubav.

336
00:30:29,920 --> 00:30:35,019
[SPEAKER_01] I što Gospodin traži od nas?

337
00:30:35,019 --> 00:30:37,039
[SPEAKER_00] The next two words, verse 5,

338
00:30:37,039 --> 00:30:39,200
[SPEAKER_00] three things.

339
00:30:39,200 --> 00:30:40,799
[SPEAKER_01] Verse 9.

340
00:30:40,799 --> 00:30:42,160
[SPEAKER_00] Verse 5, three things.

341
00:30:42,160 --> 00:30:44,660
[SPEAKER_01] Gospodin traži od nas tri stvari.

342
00:30:44,660 --> 00:30:51,839
[SPEAKER_00] On kaže, prvo spomeni se, shvati.

343
00:30:52,420 --> 00:30:56,380
[SPEAKER_00] odakle si pao.

344
00:30:56,380 --> 00:30:58,279
[SPEAKER_00] So the Lord says,

345
00:30:58,279 --> 00:31:04,599
[SPEAKER_01] kad si me isprve upoznao,

346
00:31:04,599 --> 00:31:06,220
[SPEAKER_01] bio si skroz gore na vrhu.

347
00:31:06,220 --> 00:31:10,200
[SPEAKER_01] Jer si bio jako strastven.

348
00:31:10,200 --> 00:31:14,200
[SPEAKER_01] Izgarao si od ljubavi za mene.

349
00:31:14,200 --> 00:31:15,339
[SPEAKER_00] A gospodin kaže,

350
00:31:15,339 --> 00:31:22,160
[SPEAKER_00] pogledaj gdje si pao danas,

351
00:31:22,279 --> 00:31:23,599
[SPEAKER_01] nakon 25 godina.

352
00:31:23,599 --> 00:31:25,720
[SPEAKER_00] So the first thing that we need to do

353
00:31:25,720 --> 00:31:26,940
[SPEAKER_00] is to realize.

354
00:31:26,940 --> 00:31:30,500
[SPEAKER_01] And the second.

355
00:31:30,500 --> 00:31:33,099
[SPEAKER_01] Repent.

356
00:31:33,099 --> 00:31:35,279
[SPEAKER_01] The Lord says,

357
00:31:35,279 --> 00:31:35,619
[SPEAKER_00] ok,

358
00:31:35,619 --> 00:31:37,160
[SPEAKER_00] ok,

359
00:31:37,160 --> 00:31:39,059
[SPEAKER_00] you have fallen from there,

360
00:31:39,059 --> 00:31:39,599
[SPEAKER_00] but

361
00:31:39,599 --> 00:31:41,119
[SPEAKER_01] bog kaže u redu,

362
00:31:41,119 --> 00:31:42,460
[SPEAKER_01] ti si pao dozgo,

363
00:31:42,460 --> 00:31:44,579
[SPEAKER_01] but you need to repent.

364
00:31:44,579 --> 00:31:46,180
[SPEAKER_01] Ali se trebaš obratiti.

365
00:31:46,180 --> 00:31:47,519
[SPEAKER_00] And the third thing,

366
00:31:47,519 --> 00:31:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] start doing the things you did at first.

367
00:31:53,380 --> 00:31:55,640
[SPEAKER_00] započni činiti prva djela.

368
00:31:55,640 --> 00:31:56,779
[SPEAKER_00] Now,

369
00:31:56,779 --> 00:31:59,319
