370
00:31:59,319 --> 00:32:00,420
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

371
00:32:00,420 --> 00:32:02,839
[SPEAKER_01] mi smo izgubili tu prvu ljubav,

372
00:32:02,839 --> 00:32:04,019
[SPEAKER_01] Bog to vidi.

373
00:32:04,019 --> 00:32:04,400
[SPEAKER_00] Yeah,

374
00:32:04,400 --> 00:32:06,420
