375
00:32:06,420 --> 00:32:08,500
[SPEAKER_00] three important steps.

376
00:32:08,759 --> 00:32:11,420
[SPEAKER_01] i Bog nam daje tri jako bitna koraka.

377
00:32:11,420 --> 00:32:12,539
[SPEAKER_00] Realize,

378
00:32:12,539 --> 00:32:13,579
[SPEAKER_00] shvatiti,

